@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>TechnoPagan</h1>
    <p class="lead">This is a page all about my personal path with technopaganism. Obviously in the very beginning stages.</p>
    @*<p><a href="http://asp.net" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>*@
</div>

<div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide center-div" data-ride="carousel">
    <!--INDICATORS-->
    <ol class="carousel-indicators">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
    </ol>

    <!--WRAPPER-->
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="item active">
            <img src="~/Content/book.jpg" />
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/Content/technology.jpg" />
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="~/Content/candle.jpg" />
        </div>
    </div>

    <!--LEFT AND RIGHT-->
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
    </a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" data-slide="next">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
    </a>
</div>


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>What is technopaganism?</h2>
        <p>
            To me, technopaganism is using technology to channel my intent and record my spiritual thoughts. 
            Most paganism focuses on traditional nature, but I use this to focus on the energy of humankind and what we've harnessed in electronics. 
            It might not make any sense, and others may have different definitions, but that's my current understanding of it.
        </p>
        @*<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301865">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>*@
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Why technopaganism?</h2>
        <p>
            I like witch shit and technology.<br />
            That's basically it.<br />
            I don't have the same connection to traditional Nature like most pagans do, 
            but to me technology is its own sort of energy and magic that I really connect with.
        </p>
        @*<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301866">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>*@
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>How to participate in technopaganism?</h2>
        <p>
            So many ways! Emoji spells, adding spells to your code, creating altars in games 
            or a game just for your altar, making a website like this one, etc.
        </p>
        @*<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301867">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>*@
    </div>
</div>